text:
Indian Men's National Badminton Team (sponsored by Japan's Yonex) wins the #ThomasCup 2022 defeating Indonesia 3-0 in the final in Bangkok.

Union Sports Ministry announces Rs. 1 Crore reward for the Team.

Prize Money for the winner is $120,000 (~Rs. 93 Lakh)
